tributions of architectural technology is the advancement of Building Information Modeling (BIM). BIM has transformed the design and construction process, enabling architects, engineers, and contractors to collaborate seamlessly in a shared digital environment. BIM enhances communication, coordination, and data integration throughout the project lifecycle. It allows for the creation of accurate 3D models, clash detection, quantity takeoffs, cost estimation, and efficient facility management. The use of BIM streamlines workflows, reduces errors, and improves project outcomes.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"6f03cad\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d380229\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"60b734f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"classic_columns\":\"1\",\"classic_posts_per_page\":30,\"classic_image_width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":50,\"sizes\":[]},\"classic_excerpt_length\":300,\"classic_meta_data\":[\"date\"],\"classic_meta_separator\":\"\\/\\/\\/\",\"classic_read_more_text\":\"Read More \\u00bb\",\"classic_read_more_alignment\":\"yes\",\"classic_open_new_tab\":\"yes\",\"cards_meta_separator\":\"\\u2022\",\"cards_read_more_text\":\"Read More \\u00bb\",\"full_content_meta_separator\":\"\\/\\/\\/\",\"posts_include\":[\"terms\"],\"posts_include_term_ids\":[\"11\"],\"pagination_page_limit\":\"5\",\"pagination_prev_label\":\"&laquo; Previous\",\"pagination_next_label\":\"Next &raquo;\",\"text\":\"Load More\",\"load_more_no_posts_custom_message\":\"No more posts to show\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"posts\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
