(201, 1, '2023-07-14 15:38:43', '2023-07-14 15:38:43', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">In Short</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jaiswal continued his fine run of form in the Dominica Test</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jaiswal reached his 150 in 360 balls</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jaiswal scored 15 boundaries on his way to 150</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.indiatoday.in/author/india-today-sports-desk\"><strong>By India Today Sports Desk</strong></a>: Yashasvi Jaiswal continued his fine run in the first match against West Indies as he reached the score of 150 on Friday, becoming the first Indian batter to reach the landmark in an overseas Test.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the ongoing Test match against West Indies, Jaiswal has shown remarkable skill and composure. On the second day of the Test, he scored his maiden Test century, becoming the 17th Indian Test debutant to achieve this feat. His century came off 215 balls, including 11 boundaries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'India vs West Indies Live Score, 1st Test: Yashasvi Jaiswal falls for 171; India reach 350 for 3', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'india-vs-west-indies-live-score-1st-test-yashasvi-jaiswal-falls-for-171-india-reach-350-for-3', '', '', '2023-07-14 15:38:43', '2023-07-14 15:38:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/TheMillionVoice/?p=201', 0, 'post', '', 0),
