(217, 1, '2023-07-14 16:16:41', '2023-07-14 16:16:41', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The best meal replacement shakes can be a real life saver for getting all the nutrients your body needs on the go, without having to interrupt your day to cook or prepare a full meal. While it\'s always best to get all your essential nutrients from whole foods, this isn\'t realistic for some people and the best meal replacement shakes can bridge the gap between good nutrition and convenience. If you are short on time, or have a high a calorie requirement, they’re a fast way to reach your daily calorie needs. Unlike the <a href=\"https://www.livescience.com/best-protein-powder\">best protein powder</a>, meal replacement shakes contain a range of other nutrients and functional ingredients designed to keep you full and energized when you don’t have time for a proper meal. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We take pride in testing the products in our guides ourselves, so you know you can trust our recommendations. The Live Science team taste tested the best meal replacement shakes to determine whether the taste was reflective of the advertised flavor and if there were any unpleasant aftertastes. We\'ve disregarded any products that had excessive levels of artificial sweeteners, additives or preservatives and opted for meal replacement shakes rich in natural ingredients. We\'ve covered all bases when considering the texture of the powder, testing how well it mixed into water, milk, and foods such as oatmeal or smoothie bowls. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ve also spoken to some experts in the field, including registered dieticians Alex Glover and Aisling Pigott, to answer some of your burning questions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Best meal replacement shakes 2023: Quick and easy nutrition on the move', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'best-meal-replacement-shakes-2023-quick-and-easy-nutrition-on-the-move', '', '', '2023-07-14 16